{"tid":1535470,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（行動）既然都罷搭黨鐵，不如一人做多步？","createTime":"2019-09-03T11:09:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T10:25:49.000Z","uid":170812,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"4cd127f269b728bc7f8bf15711c5ea2d5ad9c4c2","tid":1535470,"uid":170812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T11:09:04.000Z","msg":"我知唔少手足會跨欄，不過以下建議係俾罷搭黨鐵而轉搭其他交通工具嘅手足做，請體諒怕怕醜醜唔跨嘅手足。<br />\n<br />\n唔係咩大建議大行動，不過我觀察過冇乜人做。如果多人做嘅話，我相信集腋成裘。<br />\n<br />\n1.  盡量唔用八達通，多用散紙。屌八達通有過半股權都係黨鐵嘅，一樣應該要食屎！<br />\n<br />\n2. 搭其他交通工具果陣，霸<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">窗口位</span></span>，然後展示文宣，落車攞番。此謂<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">流動連儂牆</span></span>是也。成本不高，放嘅位置可以係擋到塊面嘅位置，唔怕見光。好簡單，但我相信係有效嘅。當然，要注意行車安全，唔好擋鏡，唔好擋曬全個窗。<br />\n<br />\n多謝你睇到呢度。集思廣益。<br />\n手足加油。"},{"pid":"0dd23d29dd3e254ae5e43af428014f7f6d7d2f19","tid":1535470,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T11:09:29.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"}